#	OTHER_BSS_SECTIONS - other than .bss .sbss ...
#	ATTRS_SECTIONS - at the end
#	OTHER_SECTIONS - at the end
#	EXECUTABLE_SYMBOLS - symbols that must be defined for an
#		executable (e.g., _DYNAMIC_LINK)
